subject: Re: OFFICE OF THE INVESTIGATION DE
body:
Hello  Good Day Patricia,

Your email and it contents is received, noted and well understood.
Fortunately enough the United Nation Compensation Committee on scam victim
has proposed to disburse and pay person(s) who were scammed.
All that is required of you to ensure eligibility to receive the proposed
compensation payment ($250,000) is to submit your particulars for profiling
and accreditation.
Upon receipt of your personal information, i shall forward to the National
Security Agency (NSA) in United State for Notarization/Approval.

Thanks for your patient and co-operation

John
